official_title: Assessment of Cultural Acceptability of Long Acting Contraception in a Diverse, Urban Population
inclusion_criteria:
* Between age of 18 and 45
* Not currently pregnant
* Did not participate in phase I of the study
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
Must have maximum age of 45 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Below 18 years or above 45
* Currently pregnant
* Participated in Phase I of the study
